billboard %>%
 pivot_longer(
 cols = starts_with("wk"),
 names_to = "week",
 values_to = "rank",
 values_drop_na = TRUE,
 ) %>%
mutate(week=parse_number(week)) %>%

ggplot(aes(x = week, y = rank, group = track)) +
  geom_line() +
  ggtitle("Rank vs. Week")
